  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Intimidation in Public Life: letters from Impress
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Committee on Standards in Public Life has received correspondence from Impress regarding progress made against the Committee's recommendations, following its review on intimidation in public life.</p>

  </div>
</div>

